										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國股市投資者正在關注中國人民銀行週三的下一輪利率舉措。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-43162" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CHINA-50-Daily-Chart-1.png" alt="CHINA 50 - Daily Chart" width="918" height="618" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CHINA-50-Daily-Chart-1.png 918w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CHINA-50-Daily-Chart-1-300x202.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/CHINA-50-Daily-Chart-1-768x517.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 918px) 100vw, 918px" /></p>
